    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next big adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in great shape and has been really well-loved, making it perfect for someone who wants quality without the brand-new price tag. It runs super smoothly and is comfy for those long commutes or weekend getaways. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019d love to see it go to a great home. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re going to love it!",
